text: The Lakehead University is a university in Thunder Bay, Canada. ==Faculties== Lakehead has the following faculties: *Bora Laskin Faculty of Law *Business Administration *Education Engineering *Graduate Studies *Health and Behavioural Sciences *Medical school (West Campus) *Natural Resources Management *Science and Environmental Studies *Social Sciences and Humanities ==References== ==Other websites== * https://www.lakeheadu.ca/about Category:1965 establishments in Canada Category:Thunder Bay Category:Colleges and universities in Ontario
